page.html:
18.10.2015. Kiviman turned into Kivicat.

For mania mappers
Welcome to the cute team's queue
Status: Active (1-2 mods per week)

If you need some help or advices about mapping or modding, feel free to contact me in game. But please, don't send me full mod requests there, cause i can just forget. Ask things that i can reply immediately, like checking certain pattern or playtest (6K-9K).
P.S. I like well-hitsounded maps :3

For 4K mappers: I don't mod 4K. I don't play 4K. Don't ask me for that.
Some stuff about me
Keymodes i play:
  1. 6K
  2. 7K
  3. 8K
  4. 9K


My favourite mappers:
  1. iJinjin (7K)
  2. 17VA (7K)
  3. DarkSider2442 (7K, 9K)
  4. Zenonia (7K)
  5. Kruzon (9K)


Goals in game:
  1. To complete the map for Furioso melodia
